Package org.example

Class AudioDBConnector

java.lang.Object
org.example.AudioDBConnector
public class AudioDBConnector extends Object
This class connects to audioDB API: https://www.theaudiodb.com/api_guide.php This hits up various endpoints in order to retrieve song, artist, and album information.
